Make sure you have a version of python3 installed, it may not be the main version of the MacOS since some need
older versions to run. Be sure to have pip installed, it usually comes by default with python 3.4 +
other use this documentation for help: https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/cli/pip_install/

in the terminal run:

pip3 install numpy
pip3 install pillow
